Introduction

MINIMANI (Korean: 미니마니) is a duo under CMG Stars. They debuted on June 2, 2021 with the single album, "Stop". On October 23, 2023, CMG Stars announced that MINIMANI members Han Songyi and Choi Rin is preparing to debut with a special album as a new unit, MINIMANI M, on 2023. They will make their debut in January 12, 2024 with the special album Heartbreak. On April 11, 2024, CMG Stars announced that Choi Rin had withdrawn from the group.
